<sect1 id="Filter.ScatterPlot">
	<title>Scatter Plot</title>
	<para>
		The scatter plot filter allows users to show / not show concepts
		based on attribute ranges selection in a scatter plot.
	</para>
	<para>
		Before applying the filter:
	</para>
	<para>
		<screenshot>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata fileref="../images/filter/filter_scatterPlot1.png"
						align="center" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</screenshot>
	</para>
	<para>
		After applying the filter:
	</para>
	<para>
		<screenshot>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata fileref="../images/filter/filter_scatterPlot2.png"
						align="center" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</screenshot>
	</para>
</sect1>